  "detailed_description": "Waking up in your room, you notice something. You see a small motionless doll. Her face is forever stuck screaming in terror. When you get closer, you see sharp teeth in her mouth and a knife in her hands. You push her away and run! You only have one chance to escape from this Nightmare!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hot-blooded & Addictive gameplay</h2>Stun, explode, and fire away at horrific monsters emerging from the darkness. Your survival instincts will be tested. Confront the monsters, or run and hide. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/e7238c59db0d1e1a7623998228435216.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/e7238c59db0d1e1a7623998228435216.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ever-changing Emporium</h2>Every playthrough has a unique arrangement of rooms, monsters, and items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/1d3d43792534a093abda089648f17782.webp?t=1698979186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/1d3d43792534a093abda089648f17782.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock Weapons & Relics</h2>Progression system that allows you to unlock new weapons, potions, and relics. Find and loot deadlier weapons to massacre your enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/f342ef5849bee0ec12170014b0c7ebe0.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/f342ef5849bee0ec12170014b0c7ebe0.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/f342ef5849bee0ec12170014b0c7ebe0.mp4?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Upgrades & Abilities</h2>Collect relics and potions to increase your stats and grant new abilities. Every run is unique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/9eea2ecf8e2a4bd7f6a6e614abdb1908.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/9eea2ecf8e2a4bd7f6a6e614abdb1908.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deadly Boss Battles</h2>Each floor has a unique boss battle. Find the boss’s weakness to destroy it and collect your prize. Unlock all four endings by defeating bosses.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/0ed81e99f36e1626659dcd132e1a9b8e.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/0ed81e99f36e1626659dcd132e1a9b8e.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/0ed81e99f36e1626659dcd132e1a9b8e.mp4?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Single Player<br></li><li> 60 Randomized Rooms<br></li><li> 20  A.I. Monsters<br></li><li> 40+ Relics<br></li><li> 35+ Weapons<br></li><li> 3 Boss Fights<br></li><li> 4 Endings<br></li><li> Upgrades and Unlocks<br></li><li> Readable Notes and Hints<br></li><li> Unique Puzzles<br></li><li> And more...</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Waking up in your room, you notice something. You see a small motionless doll. Her face is forever stuck screaming in terror. When you get closer, you see sharp teeth in her mouth and a knife in her hands. You push her away and run! You only have one chance to escape from this Nightmare!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hot-blooded & Addictive gameplay</h2>Stun, explode, and fire away at horrific monsters emerging from the darkness. Your survival instincts will be tested. Confront the monsters, or run and hide. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/e7238c59db0d1e1a7623998228435216.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/e7238c59db0d1e1a7623998228435216.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ever-changing Emporium</h2>Every playthrough has a unique arrangement of rooms, monsters, and items.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/1d3d43792534a093abda089648f17782.webp?t=1698979186\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/1d3d43792534a093abda089648f17782.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=200 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock Weapons & Relics</h2>Progression system that allows you to unlock new weapons, potions, and relics. Find and loot deadlier weapons to massacre your enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/f342ef5849bee0ec12170014b0c7ebe0.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/f342ef5849bee0ec12170014b0c7ebe0.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/f342ef5849bee0ec12170014b0c7ebe0.mp4?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Upgrades & Abilities</h2>Collect relics and potions to increase your stats and grant new abilities. Every run is unique.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/9eea2ecf8e2a4bd7f6a6e614abdb1908.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/9eea2ecf8e2a4bd7f6a6e614abdb1908.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deadly Boss Battles</h2>Each floor has a unique boss battle. Find the boss’s weakness to destroy it and collect your prize. Unlock all four endings by defeating bosses.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/0ed81e99f36e1626659dcd132e1a9b8e.poster.avif?t=1698979186\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/0ed81e99f36e1626659dcd132e1a9b8e.webm?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1591380/extras/0ed81e99f36e1626659dcd132e1a9b8e.mp4?t=1698979186\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Single Player<br></li><li> 60 Randomized Rooms<br></li><li> 20  A.I. Monsters<br></li><li> 40+ Relics<br></li><li> 35+ Weapons<br></li><li> 3 Boss Fights<br></li><li> 4 Endings<br></li><li> Upgrades and Unlocks<br></li><li> Readable Notes and Hints<br></li><li> Unique Puzzles<br></li><li> And more...</li></ul>",
